  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CCJPZ March 2022 By - Elections Observation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of the activities is to enable the Church to provide evidence based information on the way by-elections are conducted and to make recommendations on how credible electoral processes can be enhanced in Zimbabwe.
Overall Objective:
To contribute to a conducive environment where men and women from proclaimed constituencies and wards freely and willingly vote without fear in by-elections to be held on 26 March 2022.
Specific Objectives:
1. To train election observers and capacitate them to document pre-by election, by-election day and post by- election environment.
2. To enable the Church to authoritatively speak on the conduct of by-elections by stakeholders.
3. To make recommendations on areas that need improvement as the nation prepares for 2023 harmonized General elections.</narrative>
  </description>
